  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Breakfast</strong> is an extensive buffet with a wide selection of hot and cold dishes.  Breakfast is served on the verandas of the hotels Nautilus and Les Bouches Restaurants between 7.30am and 10.30am. </p>
<p>There are 7 onsite restaurants serving the best in traditional Sardinian cooking to the finest international cuisine there is plenty of choice with all the restaurants enjoying unique views. The restaurants offer a buffet or table service (some with a supplement)</p>]]></cateringDescription>
