  <description><![CDATA[<p>Resort Valle dell’Erica is a stunning property on the shores of Northern Sardinia, offering an oasis for both couples and families.</p>
<p>This luxury retreat is set in an exclusive and secluded park with access to pristine sandy beaches and enjoying superb views across the Meddalena Archipelago. And there are plenty of amenities and activities to ensure every guest has a memorable holiday. La Thermae Thalasso Centre and Spa is an oasis of peace in which you can relax and be pampered, the spa has special treatments that use oils enriched with locally sourced aromatic plants and four outdoor pools all heated to different temperatures. Or, you choose to unwind on the white-sand beach where comfortable loungers are available and refreshments are on offer at the sea side restaurant.</p>
<p>Families will appreciate the choice of kids’ clubs available that cater for up to 13 years. Your little ones will enjoy activities like jewellery making, swimming, football and evening shows. For families with babies, there’s even a free nursery area with everything necessary to feed your baby including bottle warming stations and vegetable purées. You can even pre-book a pushchair for no extra charge to use while in the resort.</p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Resort Valle dell'Erica is approx. 1 hour 5 mins from Olbia airport.</p>]]></description>
